DESCRIPTION:Two-Step NightFriday February 20Minimum age:All agesShow time:7:30 PMDoors open:7:00 PMLast DitchTicketsDescriptionThis event is all ages! Doors at 7pm, music and dancing at 7:30pm. $10-$15 suggested cover (pay what you can, no one turned away for lack of funds). Masks required for entry (available at venue). Elevator entry is located in the street level foyer of 10 Fiske Ave, through the glass double doors!\n\nSource: Last Ditch\n\nDetails: https://lastditchvenue.com/events-calendar#/events/169955
