LOCATION:Last Ditch\, 10 Fiske Ave\, Greenfield\, MA
DESCRIPTION:Jump In! Clown for Stage Session 3Thursday February 26Minimum age:All agesShow time:6:00 PMDoors open:6:00 PMLast DitchTicketsDescriptionJUMP IN!Clown for StageSession 3: Everything is My Partner Thursday, February 26, 2026LAST DITCH BAR, 6-9 pm $1010 Fiske Ave GreenfieldWheelchair access, open captioned, masks required and provided. Class material adjusted to needs of participants.Image description: 4 quarter image, text for event in top left & bottom right squares, white on red.  Image on top right is a figure holding a black and silver acoustic guitar against a red background. Figure wears a black and white striped blazer, a red wide collar shirt, a black duckbill n95 respirator and a theatrical mask made of paper & cardboard. It is a face with large ears, small eyes,  a deeply lined, large forehead, a red clown nose and black and white paper pompadour. The lower left image is a figure holding a guided music box against a red background. The figure wears a gauzy multicolor floral robe, a purple kn95 respirator and a theatrical mask made of paper and cardboard. The mask has a white face, heavy light blue eyelids and long black lashes, and a mane of purple, fuschia and pink paper curls.\n\nSource: Last Ditch\n\nDetails: https://lastditchvenue.com/events-calendar#/events/166128
