SUMMARY:Bratt QDP- Every Body Dance
LOCATION:Stone Church\, 210 Main St\, Bellows Falls\, VT
DESCRIPTION:Bratt QDP- Every Body DanceFriday February 27Minimum age:18 and overShow time:9:00 PMDoors open:9:00 PMStone ChurchTicketsDescriptionBQDP presentsEvery Body DanceFriday, February 27th 2026At The Stone Church210 Main St, Brattleboro, VT9p-1aBrattleboro Queer Dance Party is returning to our roots with Every Body Dance, a performance-free dance party to bring our community together through the joys of moving our bodies together while also raising funds to support the Root Social Justice Center. Featuring the beats of DJ Cartier, we invite you to bring your besties to the most supportive dance floor around and get your groove thang on!Sliding Scale $10-20notaflofThis party is for Queers and Allies ages 18+We kindly request that you wear a mask to protect yourself and others in these times of indoor entertainment\n\nSource: Stone Church\n\nDetails: https://stonechurchvt.com#/events/145088
URL:https://stonechurchvt.com#/events/145088
