DESCRIPTION:Sepsiss, Awaiting Abigail, Under The Horizon, Pulsifier GRRRLS To The Front Graduation ShowFriday March 6Minimum age:All agesShow time:7:00 PMDoors open:6:30 PMStone ChurchTicketsDescription2026 Grrrls to the Front Graduation Show!Join us as our new GTTF sound production class graduates run the show!FeaturingSepsissAwaiting AbigailUnder The HorizonPulsifierLineupAwaiting AbigailUNDER THE HORIZONPulsifierSepsiss\n\nSource: Stone Church\n\nDetails: https://stonechurchvt.com#/events/164287
