SUMMARY:Mutual Aid Open Mic! 
LOCATION:Brewbakers\, 48 Emerald St\, Keene\, NH\, 03431
DESCRIPTION:Buy Tickets on Eventbrite 
 
 Buy Tickets 
 
 
 
 
 
 The open mic will be from 7-9 pm on March 19th, right here at Nova Arts (48 Emerald St, Keene, NH 03431). Performances of music, poetry, writing, comedy, and more are all welcome. Performances should be around 5 minutes in length. For any questions, reach out to us by email at mutualaidkeene@gmail.com or on Instagram or Facebook @keenemutualaid. Sign up  HERE There is no required fee for entry to the open mic, but a donation of $5 at the door is encouraged, or you can make a digital donation via this event page as well :)\n\nSource: Nova Arts\n\nDetails: https://www.novaarts.org/events/openmic319
URL:https://www.novaarts.org/events/openmic319
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
