DESCRIPTION:&lt;p&gt;250 years ago, a new nation was brought forth by a People who had the gall to think they could govern themselves. As long as each citizen worked to improve [&hellip;]&lt;/p&gt;\n\n\nSource: Putney Library\n\nDetails: https://putneylibrary.org/event/the-pursuit-of-happiness-with-meg-mott/
