SUMMARY:New Planets
LOCATION:Stone Church\, 210 Main St\, Bellows Falls\, VT
DESCRIPTION:New PlanetsSaturday March 21Minimum age:All agesShow time:8:00 PMDoors open:7:00 PMStone ChurchTicketsDescriptionOther-Worldly, Party Music of the Past, Present, and Future, New Planets features an ever-changing lineup of singers and musicians. By combining diverse sonic stories and viewpoints, the group has gained fame for producing dance music that transcends borders and genres.LineupNew Planets\n\nSource: Stone Church\n\nDetails: https://stonechurchvt.com#/events/161825
URL:https://stonechurchvt.com#/events/161825
