SUMMARY:SARIKA with Alouette Batteau & Olivia Nied
LOCATION:Last Ditch\, 10 Fiske Ave\, Greenfield\, MA
DESCRIPTION:SARIKA with Alouette Batteau & Olivia NiedThursday April 2Minimum age:18 and overShow time:8:00 PMDoors open:7:00 PMLast DitchTicketsDescriptionAn evening of live music with Sarika, support from Alouette Batteau & Olivia Nied! This event is 18+. $12 cover (pay what you can, no one turned away for lack of funds). Doors at 7pm, music at 8pm. Masks are required for entry (available at venue). Elevator entry is located in the street level foyer of 10 Fiske Ave, through the glass double doors!\n\nSource: Last Ditch\n\nDetails: https://lastditchvenue.com/events-calendar#/events/168675
