SUMMARY:Stitch Together
LOCATION:Putney Public Library\, 55 Main St\, Putney\, VT
DESCRIPTION:&lt;p&gt;Stitch Together at Putney Library Come knit, crochet, embroider, mend or work on any handwork craft in the company of others. The library is cozy and the lighting is perfect [&hellip;]&lt;/p&gt;\n\n\nSource: Putney Library\n\nDetails: https://putneylibrary.org/event/stitch-together-11/
URL:https://putneylibrary.org/event/stitch-together-11/
