DESCRIPTION:&lt;p&gt;Do you have a pile of nice wool socks with holes, favorite jeans that would be perfect if not for a rip in the knee, or sweaters with moth holes? [&hellip;]&lt;/p&gt;\n\n\nSource: Putney Library\n\nDetails: https://putneylibrary.org/event/mending-bee-24/
