 This pass will get you into all of the music at Nova Arts on Saturday 5/16, featuring performances by Natural Information Society, Kalie Vandever, Cole Pulice, Gregory Uhlmann, Undertow Brass Band, Monadnock Music play Katie Semro, plus readings by John-Francis Quiñonez, Diannely Antigua, Jess Rizkallah, & Maya Williams. Seating is limited and first come first served. All ages. If you can pay full price, please do, but if not, use the Access for All option and pay what you can. This pass DOES NOT cover the Colonial show. To get a ticket to the Colonial show, visit them  HERE .\n\nSource: Nova Arts\n\nDetails: https://www.novaarts.org/events/thing2026saturday
