SUMMARY:John Gorka
LOCATION:Next Stage Arts\, 15 Kimball Hill Rd\, Putney\, VT
DESCRIPTION:Twilight MusicJohn GorkaSoulful, timeless folk music from a master of storytelling and song.Sunday, May 17Minimum age:All agesShow time:7:00 PMDoors open:6:15 PMNext Stage ArtsTicketsDescription$26 Advance / $30 Door / $15 Livestream“‘…the leading singer/songwriter of the New Folk movement.’ – Rolling Stone”From his early days at Godfrey Daniels in Pennsylvania to stages across the U.S. and Europe, John Gorka has built a career on soulful storytelling, masterful songwriting, and a voice that resonates with warmth and depth. With 11 acclaimed studio albums, collaborations with folk icons, and a dedication to artistic integrity, Gorka continues to captivate audiences worldwide. Join us for an unforgettable evening of timeless folk music from one of the genre’s true masters.LineupJohn Gorka\n\nSource: Next Stage Arts\n\nDetails: https://www.nextstagearts.org/events-calendar#/events/169652
URL:https://www.nextstagearts.org/events-calendar#/events/169652
END:VEVENT
